        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. The applicant Should be studying in graduate/post-graduate courses.\n1. The maximum annual income of the guardian should be ₹2,50,00/- for post-matric and ₹6,00,000/- for top class.\n1. The applicant has 40 percent or more disability.\n\n",
